        {
            "title": "全球能源危機推動需求 中國清潔科技出口激增",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Qz27NQQEZhyTkSpK2hH6QA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEABF13C_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 隨著全球市場在伊朗持續衝突及由此導致的霍爾木茲海峽中斷後轉向替代能源,中國清潔技術板塊的海外出貨量正錄得顯著增長。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>3月出口量飆升</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據中國海關總署週六發布的數據,該國3月清潔科技出口較去年同期大幅增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">太陽能電池出貨量領漲,年增80%,而電動車(EV)和鋰離子電池則分別錄得53%和34%的增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最新出口數據提供了自7週前伊朗戰爭爆發以來,中國綠色出口實力最全面的快照。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7a8ce0d6-83ff-3cae-8200-d5caab87b5f7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這場衝突實際上癱瘓了霍爾木茲海峽,引發全球能源供應危機,促使各國和各行業加速擺脫對化石燃料的依賴。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國智庫Ember的高級分析師Euan Graham指出,這波激增代表著\"僅僅是開始\",清潔技術正成為對沖燃料成本波動的關鍵手段。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>利用市場主導地位</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國已是全球電池和可再生能源供應鏈的強國,目前似乎正利用其多年來建立的產能來滿足國際需求的突然上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國內製造商已加大向海外市場的分銷力度,將綠色產品定位為國家出口增長的主要驅動力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種轉變在汽車板塊尤為明顯,根據中國乘用車協會數據,3月電動車和混合動力車出貨量達到創紀錄的34.9萬輛。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗週五晚間發出可能重新開放霍爾木茲海峽的信號,但分析師警告,航運正常化仍需數月時間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在此期間,寧德時代等主要行業參與者已報告稱,由於全球原油價格的不確定性,客戶對電動化產品的需求直接增加。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
